title: Carrot walnut cake
ingredients: ['375g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '225g butter, softened', '220g light dark brown soft sugar', '200g caster sugar', '4 eggs', '2 tablespoons orange juice', '125g chopped walnuts', '150g sultanas or raisins', '440g grated carrots', 'Icing', '225g cream cheese', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '110g butter', '160g icing sugar']
